{"tid":169056,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"達明內地歌迷：想有發聲機會","createTime":"2017-03-24T03:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T03:54:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05245f66aa5fb298a7f57f0da26cab5c8946c16e","tid":169056,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:11:43.000Z","msg":"達明內地歌迷：想有發聲機會<br />\n<br />\n娛樂要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n未夠晚上8時，已有大批歌迷排隊入場。<br />\n<br />\n達明一派一連三場「達明卅一派對」演唱會昨晚在紅館開騷，明哥因力撐雨傘運動被內地封殺，達明迷要看偶像演出，非來香港不可。來自西安的歌迷周小姐說：「自己一個人嚟，三場睇晒，上次『太平山下演唱會』有嚟睇，好鍾意佢哋作品，歌曲好有意思，打開新世界嘅門。」對於明哥被內地封殺，周小姐坦言作為內地人不想評論，但她也想有發聲機會，希望可以有接受不同聲音的機會，她說：「內地冇機會聽到明哥嘅歌、達明嘅《天問》、《十個救火的少年》都冇得聽。」<br />\n<br />\n有生之年都睇<br />\n<br />\n由上海飛來香港的葛先生表示：「鍾意咗達明七、八年，唔係好長時間，特登上海來睇騷，都知佢哋唱好多政治議題嘅歌，覺得佢哋同何韻詩嘅情況一樣。我係自己買飛嚟睇，覺得佢哋啲飛都好好賣，亦好期望佢哋能夠返內地開騷，但都相信冇乜可能。」另外，有入場歌迷表示支持達明多年，希望有生之年都會去看他們的演唱會。<br />\n採訪：盧妹<br />\n攝影：沈健程<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n不願上鏡、來自西安的周小姐，大讚達明的歌曲很有意思。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n上海歌迷葛先生希望達明能返內地開騷。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n歌迷搶紀念品　唱片最貴1750元<br />\n<br />\n娛樂要聞&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n達明一派開騷暗諷操控選舉洗腦教育<br />\n<br />\n娛樂要聞&nbsp;5小時前"},{"pid":"b85cfcff02b338f10cc2e7b66cae5b90a0fa9d78","tid":169056,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:13:06.000Z","msg":"不願上鏡、來自西安的周小姐，大讚達明的歌曲很有意思。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170324/large/24ec2p20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170324%2Flarge%2F24ec2p20.jpg&h=a9ba7d1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5b445023922dacb691351425ef9db2c80b990bb","tid":169056,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:15:37.000Z","msg":"上海歌迷葛先生希望達明能返內地開騷。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170324/large/24ec2p21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170324%2Flarge%2F24ec2p21.jpg&h=65107d80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e8fb084d4c860fe10bc9f806e850c410c7b4956","tid":169056,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:39:16.000Z","msg":"做乜post啲人個樣 佢地翻上去會比人批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e34e4ba76a996e18b5366bbb8fd57ed129c4bb","tid":169056,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:47:06.000Z","msg":"天問 歌詞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抑鬱於天空的火焰下<br />\n<br />\n大地靜默無說話<br />\n<br />\n風吹起紫色的煙和霞<br />\n<br />\n百姓瑟縮於惶恐下"},{"pid":"480ca0782eaf2218d4add5b6a2990cd9100b6000","tid":169056,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:51:36.000Z","msg":"不想評論 但又想發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ca3be770c393d93342dabed1315010b559c4ec","tid":169056,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:54:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不想評論 但又想發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反到傻撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地話不想評論，但想有發聲機會"}]}